Use Case ID: PR1

Use Case Name: Generate All Countries by Population
Created by: AG
Date Created: 14/10/2025

Actors:
User / Analyst

Trigger:
User selects “Generate All Countries by Population” from the menu.

Pre-conditions:

Database connection established.

Population data exists for all countries.

Post-conditions:

Report displayed showing all countries sorted by population (descending).

Normal Flow:

System displays report options screen.

User chooses “All Countries by Population.”

System queries database for all countries and populations.

System sorts list by population (desc).

System displays ranked results.

Extends (Alternative Flows):
E1: Sort by Population (PR8) extends at step 4 if user changes order.
E2: Generate Country Report (PR10) extends at step 5 when user selects a country.

Includes:
—
________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
Use Case ID: PR2

Use Case Name: Generate Countries by Continent by Population
Created by: AG
Date Created: 14/10/2025

Actors:
User / Analyst

Trigger:
User selects a continent and runs the report.

Pre-conditions:

Continent data available.

Countries mapped to continents.

Post-conditions:
List of countries within selected continent displayed and sorted by population.

Normal Flow:

System prompts user to select a continent.

System retrieves countries for that continent.

System sorts by population (desc).

Results displayed to the user.

Extends (Alternative Flows):
E1: Filter by Continent/Region (PR9) extends at step 1 if filter applied automatically.
E2: Sort by Population (PR8) extends at step 3 if user changes order.
E3: Generate Country Report (PR10) extends at step 4.

Includes:
—
________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
Use Case ID: PR3

Use Case Name: Generate Countries by Region by Population
Created by: AG
Date Created: 14/10/2025

Actors:
User / Analyst

Trigger:
User selects a region and runs the report.

Pre-conditions:

Region data available.

Countries mapped to regions.

Post-conditions:
Ranked list of countries in region displayed.

Normal Flow:

System prompts user to choose a region.

System fetches countries within the region.

System sorts by population (desc).

Display results.

Extends (Alternative Flows):
E1: Filter by Continent/Region (PR9) extends at step 1.
E2: Sort by Population (PR8) extends at step 3.
E3: Generate Country Report (PR10) extends at step 4.

